    <h2>Livability Score</h2>

    <script>
        const toggleTextBox = (target) => {
            let infoButton = target
            let infoBox = document.querySelector('.city-widget-info-text-box')

            if (infoButton.textContent === 'i') {
                infoButton.textContent = 'x'
                infoBox.style.display = 'block'
            } else if (infoButton.textContent === 'x') {
                infoButton.textContent = 'i'
                infoBox.style.display = 'none'
            }

        }
    </script>

    <span class="city-widget-info-button" onclick="toggleTextBox(this)">i</span>

    <span class="city-widget-info-text-box">
    The AreaVibes Livability Score evaluates 9 different categories and creates an overall score out of 100. The higher the score, the better the area.
    </span>


</div>
        <script>
    function colorMap(currentElement) {
        let category = currentElement.getAttribute('data-category')
        let attr = `data-scr-${category}`

        const mlib = maplib();
        mlib.color_map(attr)
        
        let amenities = document.querySelectorAll(`.amenity-line[data-cat='${category}']`)

        if (amenities) {
            mlib.process_amenities(amenities)
        }
    }
</script>


<div class="accordion-container">
    
<div class="widget-entry ac js-enabled" data-category="amenities" id="ac-11">

              <script>
          new Accordion('.schools-list-container', {
            elementClass: "acn",
            triggerClass: "acn-trigger",
            panelClass: "acn-panel",
            onOpen: function (currentElement) {
              colorMap(currentElement.querySelector('.acn-header'))
            },
            onClose: function (currentElement) {
              const mlib = maplib();
              mlib.color_map()
              mlib.color_no_hood_map()
              mlib.clear_amenities();
              let amenities = currentElement.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.primary-amenity')

              if (amenities) {
                mlib.process_amenities(amenities)
              }

            },
          })
        </script>

    <script>
        const toggleTextBox = (target) => {
            let infoButton = target
            let infoBox = document.querySelector('.city-widget-info-text-box')

            if (infoButton.textContent === 'i') {
                infoButton.textContent = 'x'
                infoBox.style.display = 'block'
            } else if (infoButton.textContent === 'x') {
                infoButton.textContent = 'i'
                infoBox.style.display = 'none'
            }

        }
    </script>

    <span class="city-widget-info-button" onclick="toggleTextBox(this)">i</span>

    <span class="city-widget-info-text-box">
    The AreaVibes Livability Score evaluates 9 different categories and creates an overall score out of 100. The higher the score, the better the area.
    </span>


</div>
        <script>
    function colorMap(currentElement) {
        let category = currentElement.getAttribute('data-category')
        let attr = `data-scr-${category}`

        const mlib = maplib();
        mlib.color_map(attr)
        
        let amenities = document.querySelectorAll(`.amenity-line[data-cat='${category}']`)

        if (amenities) {
            mlib.process_amenities(amenities)
        }
    }
</script>

                    <script>
                new Accordion('.amenities-list-container', {
                    elementClass: "acn",
                    triggerClass: "acn-trigger",
                    panelClass: "acn-panel",
                    onOpen: function (currentElement) {
                        colorMap(currentElement.querySelector('.acn-header'))
                    },
                    onClose: function (currentElement) {
                        const mlib = maplib();
                        mlib.color_map()
                        mlib.color_no_hood_map()
                        mlib.clear_amenities();
                        let amenities = currentElement.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.primary-amenity')

                        if (amenities) {
                            mlib.process_amenities(amenities)
                        }

                    },
                })
            </script>

        new Accordion('.amenities-list-container2', {
          elementClass: "acn",
          triggerClass: "acn-trigger",
          panelClass: "acn-panel",
          onOpen: function (currentElement) {

            colorMap(currentElement.querySelector('.acn-header'))
          },
                    onClose: function (currentElement) {
                        const mlib = maplib();
                        mlib.color_map()
                        mlib.color_no_hood_map()
                        mlib.clear_amenities();
                        let amenities = currentElement.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.primary-amenity')

                        if (amenities) {
                            mlib.process_amenities(amenities)
                        }

                    },
        })
      </script>

            new Accordion('.amenities-list-container3', {
                elementClass: "acn",
                triggerClass: "acn-trigger",
                panelClass: "acn-panel",
                onOpen: function (currentElement) {

                },
                    onClose: function (currentElement) {
                        const mlib = maplib();
                        mlib.color_map()
                        mlib.color_no_hood_map()
                        mlib.clear_amenities();
                        let amenities = currentElement.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.primary-amenity')

                        if (amenities) {
                            mlib.process_amenities(amenities)
                        }

                    },
            })

              <script>
          new Accordion('.schools-list-container', {
            elementClass: "acn",
            triggerClass: "acn-trigger",
            panelClass: "acn-panel",
            onOpen: function (currentElement) {
              colorMap(currentElement.querySelector('.acn-header'))
            },
            onClose: function (currentElement) {
              const mlib = maplib();
              mlib.color_map()
              mlib.color_no_hood_map()
              mlib.clear_amenities();
              let amenities = currentElement.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.primary-amenity')

              if (amenities) {
                mlib.process_amenities(amenities)
              }

            },
          })
        </script>

    <script>
        const toggleTextBox = (target) => {
            let infoButton = target
            let infoBox = document.querySelector('.city-widget-info-text-box')

            if (infoButton.textContent === 'i') {
                infoButton.textContent = 'x'
                infoBox.style.display = 'block'
            } else if (infoButton.textContent === 'x') {
                infoButton.textContent = 'i'
                infoBox.style.display = 'none'
            }

        }
    </script>

    <span class="city-widget-info-button" onclick="toggleTextBox(this)">i</span>

    <span class="city-widget-info-text-box">
    The AreaVibes Livability Score evaluates 9 different categories and creates an overall score out of 100. The higher the score, the better the area.
    </span>

<script>
    function colorMap(currentElement) {
        let category = currentElement.getAttribute('data-category')
        let attr = `data-scr-${category}`

        const mlib = maplib();
        mlib.color_map(attr)
        
        let amenities = document.querySelectorAll(`.amenity-line[data-cat='${category}']`)

        if (amenities) {
            mlib.process_amenities(amenities)
        }
    }
</script>

                    <script>
                new Accordion('.amenities-list-container', {
                    elementClass: "acn",
                    triggerClass: "acn-trigger",
                    panelClass: "acn-panel",
                    onOpen: function (currentElement) {
                        colorMap(currentElement.querySelector('.acn-header'))
                    },
                    onClose: function (currentElement) {
                        const mlib = maplib();
                        mlib.color_map()
                        mlib.color_no_hood_map()
                        mlib.clear_amenities();
                        let amenities = currentElement.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.primary-amenity')

                        if (amenities) {
                            mlib.process_amenities(amenities)
                        }

                    },
                })
            </script>

        new Accordion('.amenities-list-container2', {
          elementClass: "acn",
          triggerClass: "acn-trigger",
          panelClass: "acn-panel",
          onOpen: function (currentElement) {

            colorMap(currentElement.querySelector('.acn-header'))
          },
                    onClose: function (currentElement) {
                        const mlib = maplib();
                        mlib.color_map()
                        mlib.color_no_hood_map()
                        mlib.clear_amenities();
                        let amenities = currentElement.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.primary-amenity')

                        if (amenities) {
                            mlib.process_amenities(amenities)
                        }

                    },
        })
      </script>

            new Accordion('.amenities-list-container3', {
                elementClass: "acn",
                triggerClass: "acn-trigger",
                panelClass: "acn-panel",
                onOpen: function (currentElement) {

                },
                    onClose: function (currentElement) {
                        const mlib = maplib();
                        mlib.color_map()
                        mlib.color_no_hood_map()
                        mlib.clear_amenities();
                        let amenities = currentElement.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.primary-amenity')

                        if (amenities) {
                            mlib.process_amenities(amenities)
                        }

                    },
            })

              <script>
          new Accordion('.schools-list-container', {
            elementClass: "acn",
            triggerClass: "acn-trigger",
            panelClass: "acn-panel",
            onOpen: function (currentElement) {
              colorMap(currentElement.querySelector('.acn-header'))
            },
            onClose: function (currentElement) {
              const mlib = maplib();
              mlib.color_map()
              mlib.color_no_hood_map()
              mlib.clear_amenities();
              let amenities = currentElement.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.primary-amenity')

              if (amenities) {
                mlib.process_amenities(amenities)
              }

            },
          })
        </script>

                    <script>
                new Accordion('.amenities-list-container', {
                    elementClass: "acn",
                    triggerClass: "acn-trigger",
                    panelClass: "acn-panel",
                    onOpen: function (currentElement) {
                        colorMap(currentElement.querySelector('.acn-header'))
                    },
                    onClose: function (currentElement) {
                        const mlib = maplib();
                        mlib.color_map()
                        mlib.color_no_hood_map()
                        mlib.clear_amenities();
                        let amenities = currentElement.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.primary-amenity')

                        if (amenities) {
                            mlib.process_amenities(amenities)
                        }

                    },
                })
            </script>

        new Accordion('.amenities-list-container2', {
          elementClass: "acn",
          triggerClass: "acn-trigger",
          panelClass: "acn-panel",
          onOpen: function (currentElement) {

            colorMap(currentElement.querySelector('.acn-header'))
          },
                    onClose: function (currentElement) {
                        const mlib = maplib();
                        mlib.color_map()
                        mlib.color_no_hood_map()
                        mlib.clear_amenities();
                        let amenities = currentElement.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.primary-amenity')

                        if (amenities) {
                            mlib.process_amenities(amenities)
                        }

                    },
        })
      </script>

              <script>
          new Accordion('.schools-list-container', {
            elementClass: "acn",
            triggerClass: "acn-trigger",
            panelClass: "acn-panel",
            onOpen: function (currentElement) {
              colorMap(currentElement.querySelector('.acn-header'))
            },
            onClose: function (currentElement) {
              const mlib = maplib();
              mlib.color_map()
              mlib.color_no_hood_map()
              mlib.clear_amenities();
              let amenities = currentElement.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.primary-amenity')

              if (amenities) {
                mlib.process_amenities(amenities)
              }

            },
          })
        </script>

      
      <a href="/seattle-wa/lower+queen+anne/schools/" style="text-align: center;
    display: block;
    font-size: 12px;">
  See more
  Lower Queen Anne  education data
</a>
  
  <div class="widget-neighborhood-links">
    <p>Neighborhoods with high
      education scores:
    </p>
    <p>1. <a data-lat="47.640396" data-lon="-122.303947" data-ndx="4" data-scr="10" href="/seattle-wa/montlake/">Montlake (A+)</a></p><p>2. <a data-lat="47.683315" data-lon="-122.371422" data-ndx="4" data-scr="10" href="/seattle-wa/whittier+heights/">Whittier Heights (A+)</a></p><p>3. <a data-lat="47.622204" data-lon="-122.339417" data-ndx="3" data-scr="10" href="/seattle-wa/south+lake+union/">South Lake Union (A+)</a></p><p>4. <a data-lat="47.706501" data-lon="-122.298035" data-ndx="3" data-scr="10" href="/seattle-wa/meadowbrook/">Meadowbrook (A+)</a></p><p>5. <a data-lat="47.633011" data-lon="-122.283974" data-ndx="3" data-scr="10" href="/seattle-wa/madison+park/">Madison Park (A+)</a></p>  </div>

                    <script>
                new Accordion('.amenities-list-container', {
                    elementClass: "acn",
                    triggerClass: "acn-trigger",
                    panelClass: "acn-panel",
                    onOpen: function (currentElement) {
                        colorMap(currentElement.querySelector('.acn-header'))
                    },
                    onClose: function (currentElement) {
                        const mlib = maplib();
                        mlib.color_map()
                        mlib.color_no_hood_map()
                        mlib.clear_amenities();
                        let amenities = currentElement.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.primary-amenity')

                        if (amenities) {
                            mlib.process_amenities(amenities)
                        }

                    },
                })
            </script>

              <script>
          new Accordion('.schools-list-container', {
            elementClass: "acn",
            triggerClass: "acn-trigger",
            panelClass: "acn-panel",
            onOpen: function (currentElement) {
              colorMap(currentElement.querySelector('.acn-header'))
            },
            onClose: function (currentElement) {
              const mlib = maplib();
              mlib.color_map()
              mlib.color_no_hood_map()
              mlib.clear_amenities();
              let amenities = currentElement.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.primary-amenity')

              if (amenities) {
                mlib.process_amenities(amenities)
              }

            },
          })
        </script>

    <script>
        const toggleTextBox = (target) => {
            let infoButton = target
            let infoBox = document.querySelector('.city-widget-info-text-box')

            if (infoButton.textContent === 'i') {
                infoButton.textContent = 'x'
                infoBox.style.display = 'block'
            } else if (infoButton.textContent === 'x') {
                infoButton.textContent = 'i'
                infoBox.style.display = 'none'
            }

        }
    </script>

    <span class="city-widget-info-button" onclick="toggleTextBox(this)">i</span>

    <span class="city-widget-info-text-box">
    The AreaVibes Livability Score evaluates 9 different categories and creates an overall score out of 100. The higher the score, the better the area.
    </span>


</div>
        <script>
    function colorMap(currentElement) {
        let category = currentElement.getAttribute('data-category')
        let attr = `data-scr-${category}`

        const mlib = maplib();
        mlib.color_map(attr)
        
        let amenities = document.querySelectorAll(`.amenity-line[data-cat='${category}']`)

        if (amenities) {
            mlib.process_amenities(amenities)
        }
    }
</script>


<div class="accordion-container">

                new Accordion('.amenities-list-container', {
                    elementClass: "acn",
                    triggerClass: "acn-trigger",
                    panelClass: "acn-panel",
                    onOpen: function (currentElement) {
                        colorMap(currentElement.querySelector('.acn-header'))
                    },
                    onClose: function (currentElement) {
                        const mlib = maplib();
                        mlib.color_map()
                        mlib.color_no_hood_map()
                        mlib.clear_amenities();
                        let amenities = currentElement.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.primary-amenity')

                        if (amenities) {
                            mlib.process_amenities(amenities)
                        }

                    },
                })
            </script>

              <script>
          new Accordion('.schools-list-container', {
            elementClass: "acn",
            triggerClass: "acn-trigger",
            panelClass: "acn-panel",
            onOpen: function (currentElement) {
              colorMap(currentElement.querySelector('.acn-header'))
            },
            onClose: function (currentElement) {
              const mlib = maplib();
              mlib.color_map()
              mlib.color_no_hood_map()
              mlib.clear_amenities();
              let amenities = currentElement.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.primary-amenity')

              if (amenities) {
                mlib.process_amenities(amenities)
              }

            },
          })
        </script>

    <script>
        const toggleTextBox = (target) => {
            let infoButton = target
            let infoBox = document.querySelector('.city-widget-info-text-box')

            if (infoButton.textContent === 'i') {
                infoButton.textContent = 'x'
                infoBox.style.display = 'block'
            } else if (infoButton.textContent === 'x') {
                infoButton.textContent = 'i'
                infoBox.style.display = 'none'
            }

        }
    </script>

    <span class="city-widget-info-button" onclick="toggleTextBox(this)">i</span>

    <span class="city-widget-info-text-box">
    The AreaVibes Livability Score evaluates 9 different categories and creates an overall score out of 100. The higher the score, the better the area.
    </span>


</div>
        <script>
    function colorMap(currentElement) {
        let category = currentElement.getAttribute('data-category')
        let attr = `data-scr-${category}`

        const mlib = maplib();
        mlib.color_map(attr)
        
        let amenities = document.querySelectorAll(`.amenity-line[data-cat='${category}']`)

        if (amenities) {
            mlib.process_amenities(amenities)
        }
    }
</script>

                    <script>
                new Accordion('.amenities-list-container', {
                    elementClass: "acn",
                    triggerClass: "acn-trigger",
                    panelClass: "acn-panel",
                    onOpen: function (currentElement) {
                        colorMap(currentElement.querySelector('.acn-header'))
                    },
                    onClose: function (currentElement) {
                        const mlib = maplib();
                        mlib.color_map()
                        mlib.color_no_hood_map()
                        mlib.clear_amenities();
                        let amenities = currentElement.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.primary-amenity')

                        if (amenities) {
                            mlib.process_amenities(amenities)
                        }

                    },
                })
            </script>

        new Accordion('.amenities-list-container2', {
          elementClass: "acn",
          triggerClass: "acn-trigger",
          panelClass: "acn-panel",
          onOpen: function (currentElement) {

            colorMap(currentElement.querySelector('.acn-header'))
          },
                    onClose: function (currentElement) {
                        const mlib = maplib();
                        mlib.color_map()
                        mlib.color_no_hood_map()
                        mlib.clear_amenities();
                        let amenities = currentElement.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.primary-amenity')

                        if (amenities) {
                            mlib.process_amenities(amenities)
                        }

                    },
        })
      </script>

            new Accordion('.amenities-list-container3', {
                elementClass: "acn",
                triggerClass: "acn-trigger",
                panelClass: "acn-panel",
                onOpen: function (currentElement) {

                },
                    onClose: function (currentElement) {
                        const mlib = maplib();
                        mlib.color_map()
                        mlib.color_no_hood_map()
                        mlib.clear_amenities();
                        let amenities = currentElement.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.primary-amenity')

                        if (amenities) {
                            mlib.process_amenities(amenities)
                        }

                    },
            })

              <script>
          new Accordion('.schools-list-container', {
            elementClass: "acn",
            triggerClass: "acn-trigger",
            panelClass: "acn-panel",
            onOpen: function (currentElement) {
              colorMap(currentElement.querySelector('.acn-header'))
            },
            onClose: function (currentElement) {
              const mlib = maplib();
              mlib.color_map()
              mlib.color_no_hood_map()
              mlib.clear_amenities();
              let amenities = currentElement.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.primary-amenity')

              if (amenities) {
                mlib.process_amenities(amenities)
              }

            },
          })
        </script>
